        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer121808503" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12286198350348050409">This short story is quick and to the point, and absolutely hilarious! Red Chief is such a cruel little boy, but you can&apos;t help but pity him because he&apos;s so distant from his father. How O. Henry came up with such an evil little boy and yet straight forward theme is beyond my understanding.</span>
  <span id="freeText12286198350348050409" style="display:none">This short story is quick and to the point, and absolutely hilarious! Red Chief is such a cruel little boy, but you can't help but pity him because he's so distant from his father. How O. Henry came up with such an evil little boy and yet straight forward theme is beyond my understanding.</span>
